nodes.text: Two Jedi Walk Into a Bar

Two Jedi Walk Into a Bar is a scenario for the Star Wars Miniatures game, written by Tim Bresnan and published in 2005. It depicts an alternate version of Attack of the Clones, in which Obi-Wan Kenobi and Anakin Skywalker battle Zam Wesell in the Outlander Club.
The game offers rules for including neutral characters in the bar.
